# NowCare — Claude Context

AI-powered healthcare navigation platform. Patients describe symptoms → Gemini classifies urgency into one of 6 fixed care categories → app routes them to the right provider in real time. Never diagnoses. Never prescribes. Navigation only.

---

## Stack

| Layer | Choice |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React 18 + TypeScript + Vite |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS + CSS custom properties (design tokens) |
| Animation | Framer Motion (`fadeRise`, `stagger` variants in `src/lib/motion.ts`) |
| Routing | React Router v6 — nested routes, no hash routing |
| Backend | Firebase Auth + Firestore + Storage (no separate server) |
| AI | Google Gemini 2.5 Flash via `@google/genai` — called directly from browser |
| Maps | Google Maps JavaScript API |
| Provider data | NPPES NPI Registry (doctors), CMS Hospital General Info (hospitals) — both public, no API key |
| Toasts | `sonner` |
| Seed runner | `tsx scripts/seed.ts` via `npm run seed` |

