## The 6 Care Categories

Defined in `src/lib/careCategories.ts`. Used by Gemini system prompt AND the result card UI.

| ID | Headline | Urgency | Provider type |
|---|---|---|---|
| `ER_NOW` | Go to the ER now | immediate | hospital |
| `URGENT_TODAY` | See a doctor today | soon | doctor |
| `SCAN_NEEDED` | Get a scan | soon | hospital |
| `TELEHEALTH` | Try telehealth | routine | doctor |
| `SCHEDULE_DOCTOR` | Schedule with a doctor | routine | doctor |
| `SELF_CARE` | Take care at home | routine | doctor |

