## External APIs

**NPPES NPI Registry** — `https://npiregistry.cms.hhs.gov/api/?number={npi}&version=2.1`
- Public, no API key
- Used at doctor signup to verify NPI is active (`basic.status === 'A'`)
- Returns name, credential, specialty, city/state
- Stored in `/doctors/{uid}.npi_data`

**CMS Hospital General Info** — `https://data.cms.gov/provider-data/api/1/datastore/query/xubh-q36u/0`
- Public, no API key, POST with JSON body
- Used at hospital admin approval to pull CMS facility data
- Second endpoint `yv7e-xc69` for benchmarks (ER wait time `ED_1b`/`OP_18b`, imaging efficiency `OP_8`/`OP_10`)

**Google Maps JavaScript API** — key in `VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY`
- Renders `ProviderMap` with hospital + doctor pins
- Centers on `patient.lat/lng` when set

