## Hospital Portal — ER Status

ER status is **never pre-seeded**. Hospitals log in and set it manually from their dashboard via `ERStatusToggle`. It writes to `/hospitals/{uid}.er_status` and `.er_updated`. Options: `low | moderate | high | closed`. Patients see this on hospital cards in real time via `onSnapshot`.

